{"product_id":"hoia-restoring-lip-balm-with-marigold-5-5ml","title":"HOIA Restoring Lip Balm with Marigold 5,5ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA new lip balm (5.5 ml) is a particularly caring butter for lips made from organically grown marigolds in Saaremaa, to which melissa essential oil has been added as a bonus, which has a preventive effect on herpes and helps to keep the lips healthy. In the composition of lip balm you can find an as-yet unrefined deep-caring shea butter, cocoa butter and raspberry seed oil containing omega 3 fatty acids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the appropriate amount to the lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e*Butyrospermun Parkii Seed Butter, Cera Alba, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Calendula Ocinalis Flower Extract, *Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Rubus Ideasus Seed oil, *Melissa Ocinalis Leaf oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, Citral, Citronellol, Geraniol, Limonene, Linalool. *Organic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49555069075783,"sku":null,"price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-restoring-lip-balm-with-marigold-55ml-154580.png?v=1740808666","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hoia-restoring-lip-balm-with-marigold-5-5ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}